  "title": "Junior/ Senior Infrastructure Engineer - (Perm Role)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope: </strong></p><ul><li>Perform system health (such as review of OS system, application and OS backup logs) andperformance.</li><li>Perform software distribution, Operating System (OS) patching and generate patch statusreports.</li><li> Liaise with appointed agent, vendors or OEM for them to conduct troubleshooting orreplacement of hardware and software.</li><li>Provide device configuration documentation and any updates to the documentation such as maintain up-to-date network / System documentation and system inventory assets list.</li><li>Plan and configure vulnerability scanning, generation of vulnerability report status and performthe required mitigation configuration or patching.</li><li>Plan and configure backup jobs, generation of backup jobs status and perform the required mitigation configuration to resolve backup jobs issues. </li><li>To also perform recovery jobs when a change request is approved.</li><li>Perform network and application troubleshooting for system connectivity and performance issues. </li><li>Support change request for certificate renewal and provisioning and token key provisioning and perform rule configuration for cyber software.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Bachelor Degree in IT, Computer Engineering, Computer Science or related discipline</li></ul><p><strong>Technical & Functional Skill Sets: </strong><br />Virtualisation  - Nutanix, Hyper-V on Windows 11<br />Cybersecurity Tools  - Splunk Infrastructure Monitoring, Tenable Nessus<br />Hardware -  F5 appliances<br />Backup Tools - Veritas NBU<br />Operating System  - Red Hat Enterprise Linux (RHEL), Windows Server 2019 Datacenter</p><p><strong>(EA Reg No: 20C0312)</strong></p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Please email a copy of your detailed resume to <strong>abegail@talentsis.com.sg</strong> for immediate processing.</p>",
